          "reviewBody": "School has taken initiative to drive subject wise practical projects at school every month where school is giving opportunity to students to participate in groups and under the teacher guidance students have  made models and it was excellent to see various projects of SST as an interaction together ! I could see efforts put by teachers were equally appreciable and real. Every project was done at school without parents help and excellent to know teamwork and deep understanding of concept for students through such projects . I could get chance to visit it and was happy to see it",
