          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I'm Dr Vaishali Pathak mother of Archit Palshikar student of Suryadatta school.my son got admitted in Suryadatta in 2021 for 11th science in CBSE. He always wanted to pursue education in USA or UK.\nSchool staff , teachers and specially  Sheila oka madam was exceptionally supportive.\nOka mam guided from basic preparation to applications ..\nBecause of their support Archit got in worlds most renowned universities like Stanford,  Cornell  Dartmouth,  Brown and Yale.\nThis achievement could have not been possible without support of school staff and teachers and Sheila mam.\nI sincerely thank Suryadatta school for my sons accomplishments.\nI highly recommend school for all the parents who's children are aspiring for higher studies.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
